    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">You will have to calculate the average result of a roll of a certain combination of dice. You will receive a space separated list of dice in the format of <strong>1d8</strong> with 3 possible modifiers <strong>+</strong>, <strong>-</strong> and <strong>*</strong>.<br><br>The number before the <strong>d</strong> indicates how many of this die are rolled while the number behind the <strong>d</strong> is the maximum possible value. So <strong>2d6</strong> means that 2 die will be rolled with each having values between 1 and 6.<br><br>The modifiers are applied to the result of all dice rolls combined. So <strong>2d6+1</strong> would mean that 1 is added to the result of the 2 rolls added together.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> An integer <var>n</var> which indicates the number of dice rolls that will follow.<br><strong>Line 2:</strong> A space separated list <var>rolls</var> of <var>n</var> items</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> The combined average of all the dice rolls</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le; <var>n</var> &le; 50</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">1\n1d6</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">3.5</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
